The PyTestScripts is the location to add the 'Component' tests as described in the wiki
https://wiki.sophos.net/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=317105394


In order to run these tests in tap do:
 1) activate the tap environment:
    source tap/bin/activate
 2) tap run edr_plugin.component --debug-loop

In order to run them in vagrant box:
  1) ssh into vagrant
  2) Setup some links:
    a) mkdir -p /opt/test/inputs
    b) mkdir -p /opt/test/inputs/edr
    c) ln -s /vagrant/sspl-plugin-edr-component/TA  /opt/test/inputs/test_scripts
    d) ln -s /vagrant/sspl-plugin-edr-component/output/SDDS-COMPONENT/  /opt/test/inputs/edr/SDDS-COMPONENT
  3) cd /vagrant/sspl-plugin-edr-component/TA
  4) python3 -u -m pytest
  5) Result files can be seen at: /var/tmp/pytest-of-vagrant/pytest-current/sophos-splcurrent

For more information, check: https://wiki.sophos.net/display/LD/How+we+can+use+TAP+spike